## Configuration

Add the member module to your `medusa-config.ts`:

```ts
modules: [
  {
    resolve: './modules/member',
  },
]
```

## Middlewares

Add the team management middlewares to your `api/middlewares.ts`:

```ts
import { defineMiddlewares } from "@medusajs/medusa";
import { vendorMiddlewares } from "./vendor/middlewares";

export default defineMiddlewares({
  routes: [...vendorMiddlewares],
});
```

If you already have a `middlewares.ts` file, merge the middleware imports and spread them into your existing `routes` array.

